                              <locus target="#ir(ecto) #iv(erso) #42v #43v" facs="001 002 044 045">Folss. ir(ecto), iv(erso), 42v, 43v, </locus> blank, save for some scrawls on <locus target="#42v" facs="044">42v</locus>
                           </desc>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a2">
